biography_text: FINKENAUER, Abby, a Representative from Iowa; born in Dubuque, Dubuque County, Iowa, December 27, 1988; graduated from Hempstead High School, Dubuque, Iowa, 2007; attended Capitol Page School; B.A., Drake University, Des Moines, Iowa, 2011; law clerk; staff, Iowa state senate; member of the Iowa state senate, 2015-2019; elected as a Democrat to the One Hundred Sixteenth Congress (January 3, 2019-present).
